		  <p>I&#8217;m just having time to check in here and can i just say, YUM??!  I sure wish I could attend this baby shower!</p>
<p>Most of you know that my husband and I both lived in Brazil and we love love LOVE Brazilian Lemonade.  Ironically, in Brazil, they call this version &#8220;Swiss Lemonade&#8221; because of the milk in it, funny huh? We love making this for summer BBQ&#8217;s and it goes great with all types of food.  I hope you all try it!</p>
	
