		  <p>Any suggestions on making it less bitter?  I&#39;ve made it twice now and within minutes it&#39;s so bitter, it&#39;s undrinkable.  Adding sugar does not really help.  I also noticed in your pictures of the limes after they&#39;ve been blended, they were not pulvarized&#8230;.I&#39;ve read recipes for this where it says to compeltely obliterate the limes.  Could this be contributing to the bitterness?</p>
	
		  <div class="reply">
			 <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2008/05/brazilian-lemonade/?replytocom=23098#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-23098", "23098", "respond", "58")'>Reply</a>		  </div>
